title: #279: Garbage Dump, USA (@SalVulcano)
itunes:title: Garbage Dump, USA with Sal Vulcano
description: Sal Vulcano came to my apartment to enlighten me on why Staten Island isn't the worst place in America. He's a native of the land of high bangs, Italian garbage, and trash dumps. And then, I don't know how, but we got into a solid mushroom discussion in the middle of this.
